anya (1.0.2-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Release v1.0.2.
  * Added custom uninstaller wizard (--uninstall flag).
  * Added DLL and function explanations in Imports tab.
  * Added native installer branding (NSIS, DMG, Linux).
  * Added installer hardening (dependency checks, FUSE, Gatekeeper hints).
  * Added MSRV enforcement (Rust 1.85+).
  * Fixed .deb missing runtime dependencies (libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0).
  * CI consolidated from 7 jobs to 4.
  * Bug fixes and minor improvements.

 -- Daniel Iwugo <daniel@themalwarefiles.com>  Sat, 15 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

