anya (0.3.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release 0.3.2.
  * Added Bible verse CLI subcommand (`anya verse`).
  * Added ELF binary analysis support.
  * Added imphash, PE checksum validation, Rich header parsing.
  * Added TLS callback detection, overlay detection.
  * Added compiler and packer detection heuristics.
  * Added anti-analysis API detection.
  * Added MITRE ATT&CK technique tab in desktop GUI.
  * Added Teacher Mode contextual learning sidebar.

